.DT
set_max_inventory
Disk World creator help
set_max_inventory

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_max_inventory -  This method sets the maximum number of inventory items this shop will take before it starts to refuse to purchase items from players and deleting items from its inventory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_max_inventory(int i)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/general_shop.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the maximum number of inventory items this shop will
take before it starts to refuse to purchase items from players and
deleting items from its inventory.
The default for this is defined as MAX_INVENTORY in shop.h

.EP

